doesnt repeat itself and indeed they have the experience of 87 to 
draw on he told british broadcasting co televisionoin i 
think its particularly salutary that the american authorities do 
seem prepared to cut interest rates and that might help here 
analysts said the london market was concerned that a fresh burst 
of computerdriven selling on new york later monday could drag the 
