percent worldwide with increased demand for naxcel antibiotic for 
cattle and lincomix feed additive contributing 
upjohn is a worldwide provider of human and animal healthcare 
products and services as well as seeds and specialty chemicals it 
had 1988 revenues of 275 billion 
